              com.microsoft.bingads.bulk.entities.BulkLocationAdExtension

public class BulkLocationAdExtension
extends SingleRecordBulkEntity

Represents an location ad extension. This class exposes the BulkLocationAdExtension#LocationAdExtension property that can be read and written as fields of the Location Ad Extension record in a bulk file. For more information, see Location Ad Extension at http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=511515.

See Also:
BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter
